cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on video analysis and uses features from low-level and high-level video analysis. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper deals with natural language processing in the form of detecting deception in group interactions. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes an ensemble predictive model for automated deception detection. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a likely category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to develop the predictive model. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing videos in a group setting.
